{"tid":1374523,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[shall we talk] 大家發夢都好攰好辛苦, 不如我係到開個樹窿","createTime":"2019-07-27T19:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T20:20:50.000Z","uid":103829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd6a41dea38b75d0e872aa3bbf4185b5015f0ec","tid":1374523,"uid":103829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:28:24.000Z","msg":"其實好幾次發夢, <br />\n都見有人喊, 有人會不滿, 有人會對同路人破口大罵<br />\n我想係到開個樹窿,<br />\n俾大家講出發夢時既唔開心,委屈, 或者自己既苦哀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SYo0im.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SYo0im.jpg&h=7fa8c770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同大家一樣, 發夢到好攰好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到今晚我更加覺得唔開心<br />\n有朋友<span style=\"color: red;\">視死如歸</span>, 有朋友想<span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span><br />\n有個女仔想勸人走,然後我聽到有人鬧&quot;我企得上前就預左死, 咁鍾意走自己返大陸啦&quot;<br />\n<br />\n當刻我只係旁聽, 冇講過野, <br />\n其實我想同前線講: 對唔住呀, 我好廢, 我唔想死住, 但我好想幫手架..<br />\n但我亦都想同個女仔講: sorry 呀, 其實你都係想大家冇事, 我知你好唔開心.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩唔開心,不如係到講<br />\n如果係好嬲, 好不滿, 想鬧人, 冇問題, 照講<br />\n就當呢到係<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者連儂場</span><br />\n留低你心入面果句<br />\n嘗試去了解, 唔好批評<br />\n<br />\n好唔好呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3d131b71730b7d685d67e4b3e1f07794ce7879","tid":1374523,"uid":103829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"推10次冇人理就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb86682e989a51b6504c6f30038e1650310298f7","tid":1374523,"uid":103829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"推10次冇人理就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8756ea0f89aafd54c074e35ccb92f9d047d5d424","tid":1374523,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:36:56.000Z","msg":"好攰，究竟件事可以點樣完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81369faf61a56cc43f872b75d704faff962b8d11","tid":1374523,"uid":103829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8756ea0f89aafd54c074e35ccb92f9d047d5d424","tid":1374523,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:36:56.000Z","msg":"好攰，究竟件事可以點樣完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:39:54.000Z","msg":"我都好攰, 唔知幾時完<br />\n但求自己可以盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c952346276fbd71e450a41c3ced5e86faa272f8b","tid":1374523,"uid":1554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"d4236e2b8448802b18ae777daf46f999497d4fe6","tid":1374523,"uid":103829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c952346276fbd71e450a41c3ced5e86faa272f8b","tid":1374523,"uid":1554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:51:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<br />\n呢句嗌完即刻士氣+10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115c0dcd406f0d7c52448c1cd5a764f868af7fcb","tid":1374523,"uid":1554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:56:10.000Z","msg":"屌 好撚攰 12個鐘後又要上場 瞓先 巴打都早啲瞓<br />\n<br />